This nested if-else statement is a bit hard to read. Maybe we can do something like:
if (includeLocalCheck) {
    LOG.trace("Account permissioning: Checking transaction {}", transactionHash);

    boolean permitted =
        accountLocalConfigPermissioningController
        .map(c - > c.isPermitted(transaction))
        .orElse(true);

    if (includeOnChainCheck) {
        permitted = permitted &&
            transactionSmartContractPermissioningController.map(c - > c.isPermitted(transaction)).orElse(true);
    }
}

